{
  "stem": "13096.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were not allowed to go to to-- to schools that they were not run by Jewish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Jewish school itself could have only five classes, which is just the first five classes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they want us-- to humiliate us and not to-- to let us have, you know, education and to be inferior.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because in Italy, though we-- there were only all together in the whole peninsula, 40,000 Jews, but they occupied the most prominent places in the government, in science, in the university, all over the places.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were very well regarded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then they they expelled all these people after these martial laws and even the Italians had much difficulty in-- in-- in in-- in find other people to take their-- their jobs because they were really very, very clever people.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My life personally was affected because I was-- I couldn't go anymore to school and couldn't pursue my-- my studies.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the-- and I was very, very, very upset.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was crying day and night because I saw myself finish and then eventually-- eventually, well, I say I have to do something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went to the schools where I was in high school, in the [INAUDIBLE] And then there were-- the Mother Superior, they were all nuns, they say, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It will be just a matter of few-- of few months and everything will be to normal and you can come back to us because they were very understanding and very loving sisters.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So after that, you know, I went to find, to seek a job because I was not meant to stay at home and cook and bake or whatever.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I want to-- to stay, you know, with the people, you know, that were in an office.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
